        <abstract> 
<p>Is inclined to publish his "notice" after EK’s text in <hi rend="italic">Erasmus Darwin</hi>. May condense and alter it, so EK should not translate yet. As soon as Dallas finishes translating EK’s text, CD will set to work. Thinks EK’s article more interesting than what he has written.</p> 
